{"tid":1809605,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"足總本月辦四場公眾諮詢就未來發展聽取意見","createTime":"2020-01-03T08:28:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T08:57:33.000Z","uid":70063,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4e9cf1c2a1a07436f39c7096957e6084e57946c3","tid":1809605,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T08:28:49.000Z","msg":"足總將舉行四場公眾諮詢，就《展望2025策略計劃》聽取意見，諮詢會設有答問環節，公眾可於網上報名參與。<br />\n<br />\n四場諮詢會分別在本月9日、13日、16日及20日舉行，首三場以廣東話為主，最後一場則以英文形式進行，足總董事陳志康、 行政總裁溫達倫、技術總監艾拿臣等人，將分別出席各場諮詢會，講解策略計劃內容及回應提問。<br />\n<br />\n足總表示，經董事會同意下已經編寫《展望 2025 策略計劃》，定立未來十五至二十年的發展方向及展望。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500837-20200103.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500837-20200103.htm&d=GDp31xM3xvXFOTrKf8Ol7IpVoCVS%2BR9CeaLj%2Fs3YFXo%3D&h=09a03c6d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500837-20200103.htm&h=be3576c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500837-20200103.htm</a>"},{"pid":"3c8c38795762c73735843ff923347f8f70476a39","tid":1809605,"uid":7854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T08:50:26.000Z","msg":"開放本地賭球<br />\n<br />\n完"},{"pid":"eeb123e2a8d49b8a43c176be4f91b1c33a7b1422","tid":1809605,"uid":10509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T08:57:33.000Z","msg":"開賭"}]}